**Key Technologies:**

**Frontend:**
- React for web interface (consciousness-optimized design system)
- React Native for mobile apps
- Sacred geometry in visual design (golden ratio layouts)
- Accessibility-first component library

**Backend:**
- Distributed systems (no single point of failure)
- Edge computing for low latency
- Peer-to-peer architecture where possible
- Government-hosted core services with transparency

**Blockchain:**
- Custom consciousness-aware blockchain
- Proof-of-participation instead of proof-of-work
- Energy-efficient consensus mechanisms
- Quantum-resistant cryptography

**AI & ML:**
- Consciousness coherence pattern recognition
- Natural language processing for nuanced signaling
- Sentiment analysis (ethically implemented)
- Recommendation systems (explainable, non-manipulative)

**Biometric Integration:**
- Optional heart rate variability monitoring
- Voice stress analysis (for self-awareness, not surveillance)
- Facial micro-expression recognition (user feedback only)
- All biometric data processed locally, not stored centrally

